    dc:description "FIGURES 1–6. Zodarion isabellinum (Simon, 1870). 1 Male, dorsal view; 2 Female, ventral view; 3 Male palp, retrolateral view; 4 Idem, ventral view; 5 Epigyne; 6 Vulva." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4400709/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4400711>
    dc:description "FIGURES 7–14. Zodarion pallidum Denis, 1952. 7 Male, dorsal view; 8 Female, dorsal view; 9 Male palp, retrolateral view; 10 Idem, ventral view; 11 Idem, prolateral view; 12 Epigyne, ventral view; 13 Vulva, ventral view; 14 Idem, dorsal view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4400711/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4400715>
    dc:description "FIGURES 15–22. Zodarion isabellinum (Simon, 1870) (15–18) and Zodarion pallidum Denis, 1952 (19–22). 15, 19 Male palp, retrolateral view; 16, 20 Idem, ventral view; 17, 21 Epigyne; 18, 22 Vulva, ventral view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4400715/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4400719>
    dc:description "FIGURES 29–43. Genitalic morphology of Zodarion valentii Bosmans, Loverre & Addante, 2019 (29–33), Z. maculatum (Simon, 1870) (34–38) and Z. maghrebense sp. nov. (39–43). 29, 30, 34, 35, 39, 40 Male palp, ventral view; 31 Tibial apophysis, retrolateral view; 32, 33, 37, 38, 42, 43 Male palp, retrolateral view; 36, 41 Tip of embolus, ventral view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4400719/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4400727>
    dc:description "FIGURES 70–81. Genitalic morphology of Zodarion azrouense sp. nov. (70–73), Z. ericorum sp. nov. (74–77) and Z. jeanclaudeledouxi sp. nov. (78–81). 70, 71 74, 75, 78, 79 Male palp, ventral view; 72, 73, 76, 77, 80, 81 Idem, retrolateral view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4400727/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4400729>
    dc:description "FIGURES 82–93. Genitalic morphology of Zodarion mostafai sp. nov. (82–85), Z. ogeri sp. nov. (86–89) and Z. wesolowskae sp. nov. (90–93). 82, 83, 86, 87. 90, 91 Male palp, ventral view; 84, 85, 88, 89, 92, 93 Idem, retrolateral view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4400729/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4400721>
    dc:description "FIGURES 44–58. Genitalic morphology of Zodarion valentii Bosmans, Loverre & Addante, 2019 (44–48), Z. maculatum (Simon, 1870) (49–53) and Z. maghrebense sp. nov. (54–58). 44, 45, 49, 50, 54, 55 Epigyne, ventral view; 46, 48, 51, 53, 56, 58 Vulva, ventral view; 47, 52, 57 Vulva, dorsal view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4400721/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4400731>
    dc:description "FIGURES 94–109. Genitalic morphology of Zodarion azrouense sp. nov. (94–97), Z. ericorum sp. nov. (98–101), Z. mostafai sp. nov. (102–105) and Z. trianguliferum Denis, 1952 (106–109). 94, 95, 98, 99, 102, 103, 106, 107 Epigyne, ventral view; 96, 97, 100, 101, 104, 105, 108, 109 Vulva, dorsal view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4400731/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

